* === DotTalk++ regression smoke ===
* Run with:  DOTSCRIPT regression ECHO
* or from anywhere if scripts/ is on the auto search path

VERSION
DIR

* --- Color theming ------------------------------------
COLOR GREEN          && should switch to green
COLOR DEFAULT        && restore default

* --- Open sample data ---------------------------------
USE students

* --- Simple preds (predx fast-path) -------------------
COUNT FOR LAST_NAME = "SMITH"
COUNT FOR GPA >= 3.0
COUNT FOR DOB >= 20000101
COUNT ALL
COUNT DELETED

* --- Complex boolean / parens (DotTalk expr) ----------
COUNT FOR (GPA >= 3.0) AND NOT (LAST_NAME = "SMITH")
COUNT FOR (GPA >= 3.5 AND IS_ACTIVE = .T.) OR (LAST_NAME = "SMITH")
LOCATE FOR (LAST_NAME $ "MIT") OR (LAST_NAME = "SMITH")
DISPLAY                 && should show located record if found

* --- Case sensitivity toggle checks --------------------
* Expect string ops to change behavior when sensitivity flips
SET CASE SENSITIVE OFF
COUNT FOR LOWER(LAST_NAME) = "smith"
SET CASE SENSITIVE ON
COUNT FOR LOWER(LAST_NAME) = "smith"

* --- NOT / nested parens sanity ------------------------
COUNT FOR NOT (NOT (GPA >= 3.2))
COUNT FOR (STATE="CA") AND ((GPA)>=3.2)

* --- Edgey-but-safe (won't error if 0 matches) --------
* Our current policy: quotes optional* single apostrophes OK in data value
COUNT FOR LAST_NAME = "O'NEIL"     && ok even if none exist

* --- Done ----------------------------------------------
COLOR DEFAULT
